OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FNew landmark legislation to better
OL,7,Fprotect women and girls will be
OL,8,Fintroduced in Jersey after politicians
OL,9,Fvoted unanimously to approve new laws
OL,10,F(Wednesday 11 March).
OL,12,FIt means stalking and non-fatal
OL,13,Fstrangulation will be recognised as
OL,14,Fstandalone offences for the first
OL,15,Ftime, and revenge porn, deep fakes,
OL,16,Fcyber stalking and cyber flashing will
OL,17,Fnow also be criminalised.
OL,19,FSpeaking to ITV News anonymously, a
OL,20,Fwoman whom we are calling 'Daisy'
OL,21,Fdescribes being stalked two years ago.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FShe says it started with messages
OL,7,Fonline, which got more and more
OL,8,Fthreatening. 'Daisy' explains: "I
OL,9,Fremember I was walking to work, and I
OL,10,Fsaw him behind me, so I got my phone
OL,11,Fand called my parents straight away. I
OL,12,Fremember saying, I think he's behind
OL,13,Fme, he's behind me. I was shaking"
OL,15,FIt comes after Jersey's Justice and
OL,16,FHome Affairs Minister lodged "key
OL,17,Flegislation" to tackle violence
OL,18,Fagainst women and girls (VAWG) in
OL,19,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FThe amendments expand definitions and
OL,7,Fcreate new offences to hold
OL,8,Fperpetrators to account, from sharing
OL,9,Fintimate images of another person
OL,10,Fwithout their consent, to stalking and
OL,11,Fstrangulation.
OL,13,FThere were 192 reports of stalking
OL,14,Fissued between 2016 and 2021, but only
OL,15,Ftwo resulted in convictions.
OL,17,FHowever, under new laws, those
OL,18,Fconvicted could be jailed for five
OL,19,Fyears and fined, or 10 years for
OL,20,Faggravated stalking offences.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FStalking behaviour includes tracking a
OL,7,Fperson's movements, including their
OL,8,Fcommunications, messaging, giving
OL,9,Fgifts or accessing their social media
OL,10,Faccounts and loitering near someone's
OL,11,Fpremises.
OL,13,FIt also includes aggravated stalking,
OL,14,Fwhereby the behaviour causes someone
OL,15,Fto fear that violence will be used
OL,16,Fagainst them or if they experience
OL,17,Fserious anxiety or distress, which
OL,18,Finterrupts everyday life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FThe law also specifically
OL,7,Fdistinguishes harassment from
OL,8,Faggravated harassment, whereby
OL,9,Faggravated harassment is recorded when
OL,10,Fsomeone's repeated actions cause a
OL,11,Fvictim to fear violence, or create
OL,12,Fsuch high levels of alarm and distress
OL,13,Fthat it interferes with their day-to-
OL,14,Fday activities.
OL,16,FRecalling her experience of stalking,
OL,17,F'Daisy' says it started with a message
OL,18,Frequest on social media: "I am private
OL,19,Fon the social media he contacted me
OL,20,Fon, and I happened to check my message
OL,21,Frequests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"It started off nicely with nice
OL,7,Fmessages, then it took a turn. The
OL,8,Ffirst message was telling me how
OL,9,Fbeautiful I was, that I was the most
OL,10,Fbeautiful person he had ever seen, but
OL,11,FI just didn't think anything of it. I
OL,12,Fdidn't open or accept the request; I
OL,13,Fjust left it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"Then I checked my requests again, and
OL,7,Fthere were two other messages from
OL,8,Fhim, this time a lot more threatening,
OL,9,Fand this is where I started to get
OL,10,Fconcerned. But then again, I thought
OL,11,Fnothing of it. I'm from the UK, and
OL,12,Fthis type of thing happens all the
OL,13,Ftime; all my friends get these types
OL,14,Fof messages.
OL,16,F"It wasn't until my friend dropped me
OL,17,Foff at home from work and I checked my
OL,18,Frequests that's when I saw the next
OL,19,Fmessage. It said, 'I see you every day
OL,20,Fgetting in and out of that car, next
OL,21,Ftime wait for me.' "
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FThe messages read:
OL,8,F"Hey, I can't remember the last time I
OL,9,Fsaw someone as beautiful as you."
OL,11,F"See you every day getting in and out
OL,12,Fof that car. Next time, wait for me."
OL,14,F"The f*** you doing here without
OL,15,Fgiving me head."
OL,17,F'Daisy' describes how the messages
OL,18,Fmade her feel, she says: "I was
OL,19,Fimmediately scared, and you know, I
OL,20,Fwas new to this island. I had no
OL,21,Ffamily or anyone to turn to.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"I then remember I was walking to work
OL,7,Fand I saw him behind me, so I actually
OL,8,Fgot my phone and called my parents
OL,9,Fstraight away. I remember saying, I
OL,10,Fthink he's behind me, he's behind me.
OL,12,F"From that point, I was just on edge
OL,13,Fat all times.
OL,15,F"It was frightening, if I were walking
OL,16,Fhome, going anywhere, I'd have to call
OL,17,Fmy mum or my dad or anyone."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F'Daisy' continues: "What's frightening
OL,7,Fis that because it was a message
OL,8,Frequest on social media, and I had to
OL,9,Ffind the message, I actually have no
OL,10,Fidea how long this person was watching
OL,11,Fme or following me."
OL,13,FAfter feeling too scared to go out,
OL,14,Fshe then called the police. 'Daisy'
OL,15,Fexplains: "I remember the first call I
OL,16,Fhad with the police was with a male
OL,17,Fofficer, and actually, I thought it
OL,18,Fwas quite submissive.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"It wasn't until I was passed on to a
OL,7,Ffemale officer that I felt I was being
OL,8,Ftaken seriously."
OL,10,FShe says her stalker was never
OL,11,Fprosecuted, and instead, the police
OL,12,Fknocked on his door to warn him to
OL,13,Fstay away.
OL,15,FWhen asked if 'Daisy' felt the police
OL,16,Fdid enough, she responds: "No, because
OL,17,Fwhat if he got angry at that and so
OL,18,Fthought, 'well, I know where she
OL,19,Flives, she's just told on me
OL,20,Fessentially, and so did something to
OL,21,Fme?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"Why should it take something to
OL,7,Fhappen to someone for us to wake up
OL,8,Fand decide that we need to do
OL,9,Fsomething about this?"
OL,11,F"I think what is stark is that so many
OL,12,Fwomen ignore messages like these,
OL,13,Fbecause we are just used to them, but
OL,14,Fwhy is that acceptable?"
OL,16,FJersey's Detective Superintendent,
OL,17,FAlison Fossey, welcomes the bill but
OL,18,Fsays the laws will require specialist
OL,19,Fstaff.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FShe explains: "This needs to be
OL,7,Fresourced. We need to recruit
OL,8,Fspecialists, investigators who are
OL,9,Fgoing to look at that extra demand,
OL,10,Fand that's on top of the fact that we
OL,11,Falready have a 25% increase in VAWG
OL,12,F(Violence against women) offences
OL,13,Fbeing reported to us.
OL,15,F"I am really pleased, we welcome the
OL,16,Flegislation which modernises a lot of
OL,17,Foffences which we do have in Jersey,
OL,18,Fbut in other names.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"For example, non-fatal strangulation
OL,7,Fcan sometimes account for grave and
OL,8,Fcriminal assault, but this legislation
OL,9,Fidentifies these offences in their own
OL,10,Fright and treats them with the
OL,11,Fseriousness they deserve, which is a
OL,12,Fgood thing because it raises awareness
OL,13,Fand encourages more people to come
OL,14,Fforward."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,FShe continues: "One of the big bonuses
OL,7,Fof this new legislation for us is the
OL,8,Fintroduction of prevention orders, for
OL,9,Fexample, stalking, stalking prevention
OL,10,Forder, which lets us nip behaviour in
OL,11,Fthe bud early on and prevent offenders
OL,12,Fearly on from going on to commit,
OL,13,Fsometimes, very serious offences.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"We have never had these prevention
OL,7,Forders before in Jersey, so in
OL,8,Faddition to stalking, we are also
OL,9,Fgetting emergency barring, notices and
OL,10,Forders with regards to domestic abuse,
OL,11,Fand that is really important for us to
OL,12,Fkeep victims safe and prevent
OL,13,Foffenders from offending."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F"There needs to be a big education
OL,7,Fpackage that goes alongside the
OL,8,Fintroduction of this legislation, so
OL,9,Fthat the public and all the agencies
OL,10,Fthat support victims of these types of
OL,11,Fcrimes, ourselves, they'll need to be
OL,12,Fa big investment in training, for
OL,13,Fourselves as well.
OL,15,F"Investment is needed, of course,
OL,16,Fbecause we don't want to set up all
OL,17,Fthese new laws, raise expectations and
OL,18,Fthen provide a service that doesn't
OL,19,Fmatch those expectations."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G17/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1773425166
OL,3,CJersey passes 'landmark' laws for
OL,4,Cstalking and non-fatal strangulation
OL,6,F'Daisy' says if she could send a
OL,7,Fmessage to her stalker, she would say:
OL,8,F"You get to get on with your life, I
OL,9,Fdon't. I am left constantly looking
OL,10,Fover my shoulder.
OL,12,F"How dare you think you can send me
OL,13,Fmessages like that? How dare you think
OL,14,Fyou can send me messages like that,
OL,15,Fhow dare you ruin my island experience.
OL,17,F"I now walk the streets scared, I am
OL,18,Fconstantly looking over my shoulder
OL,19,Ffor people like you, I am looking for
OL,20,Fyour face in a crowd, how dare you
OL,21,Fstrip my freedom almost away from me."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G18/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
